ent-WeaponGrapplingGunHunter = STU "Grappler"
    .desc = A Nanotrasen service capture device: a two-handed U-frame with webbing net. Fires a tethered line that cinches targets for safe detainment. Most effective at short range; non-lethal and rough on dignity.
ent-WeaponGrapplingGunHunterSyndicate = STU "Grappler-E"
    .desc = A Syndicate contraband variant of the Grappler with an integrated shock pack. After capture it sends a jolt down the line to stun the mark for rapid extraction. Limited charges; unlimited legal risk.
